node.text: Zoe Kravitz's clap back when someone criticized her see-through dress has us on our feet. 👏 Her perfect response is at the link in our bio. (📷: Getty)

node.text: Not everybody loved Patricia Heaton as Debra on #EverybodyLovesRaymond. The show's creator revealed the network requested someone "hotter"—and he almost quit the show over it. 👀 Link in bio. (📷: Getty)
